    Camilo "De Adentro Pa Afuera"
    Dolby Atmos Music



    De adentro pa afuera (stylized as DAPA)1 is the third studio album by Colombian singer Camilo.

    The album is characterized by Camilo's varied musical style, where there is a fusion with rhythms such as reggaeton, pop, cumbia villera, bachata and regional Mexican, among others. Also on September 6, 2022, the album was released along with its single "Airport"2.

    From this album, some hits emerge such as: "Pesadilla", "Pegao", "Alaska" and "NASA" among others. This album includes the participation of Alejandro Sanz, Evaluna Montaner, Grupo Firme and Nicki Nicole among others. Some of the singles featured the direction and acting participation of Evaluna, while "Indigo" was presented as part of the news of Evaluna's pregnancy.

    Big Bad Beetleborgs (despus Beetleborgs Metallix) es una serie de televisin estadounidense de los aos 90 del genero accin, aventura y comedia, creada por Haim Saban y producida por Saban Entertainment para Fox Kids Network.
    Transmitida durante dos temporadas por la cadena FOX, a traves de su bloque de Fox Kids entre septiembre de 1996 y marzo de 1998.
    -
    Temporadas: 2
    Episodios: 88
    Pais: USA
    Duracin Ep: 33 Min

    Laura Pausini "Las cosas que vives"
    Dolby Atmos Music



    Le cose che vivi (en espaol: Las cosas que vives) is the third studio album and the second album in Spanish by the Italian singer Laura Pausini and the most sold in her disco career. Released in 1996 by Warner Music. It was the disco that confirmed the singer's success abroad, selling more than 10 million copies.34 El 12 de septiembre de 1996 el disco fue publicado en treinta y siete pases.5 Later, el 9 de diciembre del mismo ao Las cosas que vives se public para Espaa y toda la regin de Amrica Latina.
